         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">17/11/87 ¶  ¶ I am pleased, dear Mr Tepper, that you intend to give me the opportunity to figure  ¶ Acacia rhigiophylla ¶ . ¶  ¶ The little plant sent recently is a  ¶ Helipterum ¶  closely related to...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">87.11.17b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">17/11/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es freuet mich, lieber Herr Tepper, dass Sie mir die Gelegenheit geben wollen, die <name key="Acacia%20rhigiophylla">Acacia rhigiophylla</name> abzubilden.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Das jüngst gesandte Pflänzchen ist ein Helipterum nahe mit H. pygmaeum verwandt. Die Exemplare sind noch zu jung, um etwas Ordentliches damit zu machen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die Benennung der W.A. Pflanzen soll geschehen, wenn der Key fertig ist</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Bestens grüssen</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">17/11/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am pleased, dear Mr Tepper, that you intend to give me the opportunity to figure <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Acacia%20rhigiophylla">Acacia rhigiophylla</name>
               </seg>.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to O. Tepper, 7 November 1887 (in this edition as 87-11-07a), and M to O. Tepper, 26 November 1887 (in this edition as 87-11-26b).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The little plant sent recently is a <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Helipterum</seg> closely related to <seg style="font-style: italic; ">H. pygmaeum</seg>. The specimens are still too young to make anything substantial of it.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The naming of the Western Australian plants will happen when the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Key</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B88.11.02.</p>
               </note> is finished.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Best greetings</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Acacia%20rhigiophylla">Acacia rhigiophylla</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Helipterum%20pygmaeum">Helipterum pygmaeum</name>
            </p>
         </div>
